  "title":       "Tinted Images",
  "url":         "/blog/tinted-images/",
  "permalink":   "http://localhost:1313/blog/tinted-images/",
  "date":        "2025-01-10",
  "tags":        ["palette","images"],
  "summary":     "Monochrome images tinted to any base16 colour with CSS mask-image.",
  "readingTime": 1,
  "content":     "\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ccode\u003etinted-image\u003c/code\u003e shortcode recolours monochrome images (SVG, PNG) to\nany palette slot using CSS \u003ccode\u003emask-image\u003c/code\u003e. No JavaScript, no\napproximation — the colour is an exact CSS custom property.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"single-colour\"\u003eSingle colour\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n     role=\"img\"\n     aria-label=\"Terminal\"\n     style=\"\n       background-color: var(--base0D);\n       -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n       mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n       width: 64px;\n       height: 64px;\n     \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"chroma\"\u003e\u003ccode class=\"language-go-html-template\" data-lang=\"go-html-template\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cp\"\u003e{{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"err\"\u003e\u0026lt;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003etinted\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"err\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eimage\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003esrc\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;/images/terminal.svg\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ecolor\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;base0D\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ewidth\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;64px\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eheight\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;64px\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"err\"\u003e\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cp\"\u003e}}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"palette-sampler\"\u003ePalette sampler\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe same image in every accent colour:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:1rem; align-items:center; margin:1rem 0;\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Red\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base08);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Orange\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base09);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Yellow\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0A);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Green\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0B);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Cyan\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0C);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Blue\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0D);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Purple\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0E);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Brown\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0F);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/terminal.svg');\n         width: 48px;\n         height: 48px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"different-shapes\"\u003eDifferent shapes\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAny monochrome image works — opaque pixels become the tinted colour,\ntransparent pixels stay transparent.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:1.5rem; align-items:center; margin:1rem 0;\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Code\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0B);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/code.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/code.svg');\n         width: 56px;\n         height: 56px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Gear\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base09);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/gear.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/gear.svg');\n         width: 56px;\n         height: 56px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Globe\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base0C);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/globe.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/globe.svg');\n         width: 56px;\n         height: 56px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"tinted-image\"\n       role=\"img\"\n       aria-label=\"Heart\"\n       style=\"\n         background-color: var(--base08);\n         -webkit-mask-image: url('/images/heart.svg');\n         mask-image: url('/images/heart.svg');\n         width: 56px;\n         height: 56px;\n       \"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-it-works\"\u003eHow it works\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe image acts as an alpha mask on a coloured \u003ccode\u003e\u0026lt;div\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"chroma\"\u003e\u003ccode class=\"language-css\" data-lang=\"css\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nc\"\u003etinted-image\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003ebackground-color\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nf\"\u003evar\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e--\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"n\"\u003ebase0D\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e);\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003emask-image\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003eurl\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u0026#39;/images/logo.svg\u0026#39;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e);\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003emask-size\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"kc\"\u003econtain\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003emask-repeat\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"kc\"\u003eno-repeat\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eOpaque pixels → colour shows. Transparent pixels → nothing renders.\nSwap the palette and every tinted image updates instantly.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"parameters\"\u003eParameters\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdl class=\"info-list\"\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003esrc\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003ePath to a monochrome image (required)\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003ecolor\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eBase16 slot name, e.g. \u003ccode\u003ebase0D\u003c/code\u003e (default: \u003ccode\u003ebase0D\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003ealt\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eAccessible label\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003ewidth\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eCSS width (default: \u003ccode\u003eauto\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/dd\u003e\n  \u003cdt\u003e\u003ccode\u003eheight\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/dt\u003e\u003cdd\u003eCSS height (default: \u003ccode\u003eauto\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/dd\u003e\n\u003c/dl\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBest results with images that are solid white (or any opaque colour) on\na transparent background. SVGs work perfectly; PNGs need an alpha channel.\u003c/p\u003e\n"
}
]
